data.description: Home Sweet Home! This 3 bedroom Ranch has over 1450 square feet with a spacious fenced in back yard and work shed. With original wood floors in areas of home and beautiful fireplace, this a must see! Come into your lovely living room space, office or even just a great chill room. To the right you will have all your great sized bedrooms and straightforward you'll enter the large kitchen with breakfast area. After the kitchen you'll have a HUGE den with stunning fireplace to relax and enjoy the days to come. The backyard is a great size to entertain and has a shed as well. Come check this one out today!
